content:
Navigate Revenue Insights Dashboards More Easily

You can move quickly between your dashboards and insights with tabs across the top of your Revenue Insights app. You can also pin your preferred dashboard so that it opens automatically.

Where: This change applies to Sales Cloud in Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions for an additional cost.

From the Sales app navigation bar, find Revenue insights, and open it. View your dashboards and insights tabs across the top of the screen.
title: Easily Navigate Salesforce Revenue Insights Dashboards
